\n嬲到紅都臉曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係又乜都做唔到 就好似成個水吧俾人強暴咁<br />\n<br />\n當我飲完一杯又一杯 將每一塊檸檬嘅汁液都揸到盡曬 條水吧佬已經激到要人幫手扶住<br />\n而我就露出勝利者嘅表情 行去收銀機俾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係個一刻 我知我已經贏曬 準備去下一間茶記繼續開檸茶party<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T15:02:29.000Z","msg":"飲撚到糖尿病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50a5a680a61cefb98a73a12a77bd4c53ac2414e0","tid":759284,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T15:07:58.000Z","msg":"如果呢度無得添飲檸檬茶 呢度以後都無得添飲檸檬茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"829910458c97ec3f91b9920953f247ccd2b03e70","tid":759284,"uid":66870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T15:42:53.000Z","msg":"而家先知？"},{"pid":"0549c71d050e4f78b0a497aeeccdb3ed581790f7","tid":759284,"uid":90457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c180ab79f0959afe1b614a87c06c151fc5892efc","tid":759284,"uid":175683,"like":99,"dislike":9,"score":90,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T12:56:30.000Z","msg":"樓主飲凍檸茶落砂糖？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T15:46:59.000Z","msg":"有乜問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a895c1ca1a67a6d4820f904eb6e9ca5ff05391e","tid":759284,"uid":144711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T16:16:24.000Z","msg":"好心你啦 咪咁乞兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dcccb8ec341d30d4284069580d06aaada6c4237","tid":759284,"uid":47824,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"cited